They are anarchists to be sure, bent{Newline}
on bringing down the aristocracy.{Newline}
{Newline}
But they fancy themselves righteous,{Newline}
and prey only on the nobility and{Newline}
those in our employ.{Newline}
Would such as they truly kidnap the{Newline}
marquis for want of coin?
