{Color 00}Why have you kidnapped this girl?
{MClose}
{Color 08}Gragoroth{Newline}
{Color 00}We had to take a hostage—there was{Newline}
no other way to escape.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Wiegraf{Newline}
{Color 00}Then why not release her once you{Newline}
were clear of your pursuers?{Newline}
Do not tell me this madness has taken{Newline}
even you!
{MClose}
I am no Gustav, if that is your fear!{Newline}
{Newline}
{Newline}
Think, Wiegraf. We've lost the greater{Newline}
part of our number, and the Northern{Newline}
Order draws upon us from all sides.{Newline}
She is of Beoulve blood. A hundred{Newline}
swords—a thousand!—could not buy{Newline}
our freedom with such ease!
{MClose}
So we fly—what then? Know you some happy{Newline}
haven in which we may alight?{Newline}
{Newline}
If we flee, they win once more. As they{Newline}
have always won.{Newline}
{Newline}
We must make for our children a fairer{Newline}
future than the past you and I have known.{Newline}
They must not suffer as we do!{Newline}
The stone we cast might raise only the{Newline}
smallest of waves, but see how they crash{Newline}
upon the shore!{Newline}
Waves rich with our blood...
{MClose}
Then you order us to our deaths!?
{MClose}
If by our deaths a single drop of noble{Newline}
blood should water the earth, they shall{Newline}
not be in vain.
{MClose}
Foolishness! The only blood the earth{Newline}
will drink will be our own.
{MClose}
The remainder of our forces should yet{Newline}
be safe in our fastness at Ziekden.{Newline}
{Newline}
We must rejoin them—together we{Newline}
have the strength to strike!
{MClose}
And if they are already dead?
{MClose}
Milleuda? Slain?{Newline}
Impossible...
{MClose}
The company which slew her{Newline}
must approach even now.{Newline}
{Newline}
Your orders, Commander?
{MClose}
We quit this place at once!{Newline}
{Newline}
{Newline}
We shall make for our fastness at{Newline}
Ziekden. The girl will be left here,{Newline}
Gragoroth.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Lookout{Newline}
{Color 00}The Northern Sky is upon us!{Newline}
They attack!
{MClose}
They waste little time.{Newline}
{Newline}
{Newline}
I shall hold them off here!{Newline}
Gragoroth, you will take the{Newline}
others and make for Ziekden!
{MClose}
I will run, yes. But I{Newline}
do not mean to die!
{MClose}
