used in the help messages.{Newline}
{Newline}
{Color 08}Range{Color 00} is the attack range.{Newline}
{Color 08}Radius{Color 00} is the radius of the area of effect.{Newline}
{Color 08}MP{Color 00} is the number of MP consumed.{Newline}
{Color 08}Speed{Color 00} is the ability's Speed attribute.{Newline}
☇ means that the magick may be reflected{Newline}
by the Reflect ability.{Newline}
"Arithmeticks" indicates a spell that may be{Newline}
used with arithmeticks.{Newline}
{Newline}
{Color 08}Removes{Color 00} indicates status effects that{Newline}
the ability removes.{Newline}
{Color 08}Effect{Color 00} is the inflicted status effect.{Newline}
