{Color 08}Folmarv{Newline}
{Color 00}I fear I've no more time to waste on you.{Newline}
{Newline}
Would that I could bid you farewell here,{Newline}
but I suspect you'd not part ways so{Newline}
easily.{Newline}
I suppose you must be returned to the{Newline}
Father after all. My thralls will delight to{Newline}
guide you to His keeping.{Newline}
This sanctuary even holds a sarcophagus.{Newline}
It's as though Fate lends her hand!
{MClose}
Of course, death is sooner served{Newline}
by steel. I shall let this one be your{Newline}
foeman as well.
