{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
Good day to you. Might I interest you in a{Newline}
drink?
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
Mayhap you might. Have you any milk?
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
Ha! I like you already! I've not had a customer{Newline}
order milk before.{Newline}
You've seen your share of battle, have you{Newline}
not? Most men as live that sort of life come{Newline}
wanting spirits.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
You mean to say the stories were true?{Newline}
There are monsters in Gollund?
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
Hordes of them, causing all sorts of trouble.{Newline}
They had to close the mines.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
Times as these, knights are too busy slaying{Newline}
each other to deal with beasts.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
The town's raised a call for hunters.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
You can swing a sword, aye?{Newline}
There's coin to be had in this.
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
I care not for coin. I would go to aid{Newline}
the people in their plight.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
A man of honor, are we? Few enough of{Newline}
those these days.{Newline}
If only Lord Barbaneth were still alive!{Newline}
He'd do something about it.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
As I was meaning to say, though, there's{Newline}
one among 'em no hunter can best.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
A keen one, eh? What manner of beast?
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavern Patron{Color 00}{Newline}
A beast of legend—the Holy Dragon.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
You mean to go?
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
Yes—at least to know if the talk is true.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Tavernmaster{Color 00}{Newline}
Gods be with you, then.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Swordsman{Color 00}{Newline}
If you leave for the mines of Gollund, would{Newline}
you not hire my sword to accompany you?
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
I do not believe we've made acquaintance.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Swordsman{Color 00}{Newline}
I am Beowulf—a hunter.{Newline}
{Newline}
I pursue the Holy Dragon of which they speak.{Newline}
It has been my purpose for many a year.{Newline}
{Newline}
My knowledge of her would surely be a boon.{Newline}
What say you?
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
{Begin List}1. I've no need of hired steel.{Newline}
2. How much gil does your blade require?{End List}
{AClose}
