{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
I do not believe we've made acquaintance.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Swordsman{Color 00}{Newline}
I am Beowulf—a hunter.{Newline}
{Newline}
I pursue the Holy Dragon of which they speak.{Newline}
It has been my purpose for many a year.{Newline}
{Newline}
My knowledge of her would surely be a boon.{Newline}
What say you?
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
{Begin List}1. I've no need of hired steel.{Newline}
2. How much gil does your blade require?{End List}
{AClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
My apologies, but I've no need of hired steel.
{MClose}
{Color 08}Beowulf{Color 00}{Newline}
I see. Most unfortunate. Good-bye, then—and{Newline}
fare-well.
{MClose}
{Color 08}{Ramza}{Color 00}{Newline}
Very well. How much gil does your blade{Newline}
require?
{MClose}
{Color 08}Beowulf{Color 00}{Newline}
We can speak of coin when the job is done.{Newline}
Come, let us make for Gollund.
{MClose}
